66
00:04:12,360 --> 00:04:13,760
Major!

67
00:04:19,890 --> 00:04:21,490
You will return...

68
00:04:21,980 --> 00:04:24,110
Alphonse Elric to me.

69
00:04:26,030 --> 00:04:30,740
My word... 
Sloth sure is a slave driver.

70
00:04:31,060 --> 00:04:34,920
Then again, she was responsible for letting him escape,

71
00:04:34,920 --> 00:04:36,380
so I guess she has no choice.

72
00:04:37,220 --> 00:04:40,300
So, what will you do, Greed?

73
00:04:51,980 --> 00:04:53,020
You see that?

74
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:56,860
That is the artistic alchemy that has been passed down

75
